data.description: This 3-bedroom 2 bath features newer laminate flooring, new windows and an abundance of natural light throughout the home. The fridge, washer, and dryer are all included. It is centrally located and close to HWY 395 for an easy commute! It's also only 8 minutes from UNR! It sits on .37 (1/3) of an acre and has a lovely covered patio in the backyard.  The large lot has RV access and separate access for a boat, camper, trailer, or extra parking.
